Hoisting 

•The variable deceleration and function deceleration will move to the top of the scope.
•Hoisting will be applicable for var variable
only not for let and const.

TDZ - temporal dead zone

* when we declare the variable with let and const without us proper initialization then the variable lies in temporal dead zone until its proper initialization. 
